1
00:00:03,290 --> 00:00:05,670
That scared me half to death! This is bad!

2
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:17,960
That was incredible!

3
00:00:18,250 --> 00:00:19,250
Huh?

4
00:00:20,500 --> 00:00:21,500
It's okay.

5
00:00:22,540 --> 00:00:23,540
Sami...

6
00:00:25,040 --> 00:00:27,920
Take care of yourself.
And be happy.

7
00:00:29,500 --> 00:00:30,500
You too, Reika.

8
00:00:31,380 --> 00:00:32,540
Come on, smile.

9
00:00:33,830 --> 00:00:35,540
But I am happy!

10
00:00:36,750 --> 00:00:38,380
I'm sorry.

11
00:00:38,380 --> 00:00:39,710
I knew it. I can't do it.

12
00:00:42,540 --> 00:00:43,540
No...

13
00:00:43,540 --> 00:00:44,880
I can't bring myself to say it.

14
00:00:45,710 --> 00:00:47,670
I don't want to leave you...

15
00:00:51,670 --> 00:00:52,670
Sami.

16
00:00:58,080 --> 00:01:00,040
You remember
our promise, don't you?

17
00:01:00,790 --> 00:01:01,790
Yes.

18
00:01:03,460 --> 00:01:04,460
I'm prepared.

19
00:01:05,880 --> 00:01:06,210
Yes.

20
00:01:06,210 --> 00:01:09,000
No!
I'm talking about a much older promise.

21
00:01:09,790 --> 00:01:11,080
A much older one?

22
00:01:11,250 --> 00:01:12,540
We made a promise a long time ago,
didn't we?

23
00:01:13,250 --> 00:01:14,960
That whatever becomes
an obstacle in your life...

24
00:01:14,960 --> 00:01:16,290
I will eliminate it.

25
00:01:17,960 --> 00:01:21,250
It seems that obstacle...
is me.

26
00:01:22,580 --> 00:01:24,000
I'm going to keep that promise.

27
00:01:26,830 --> 00:01:30,460
I... I'll step aside.
